profile:
Maritime Garage Doors is a garage door specialist for residential, commercial, agricultural and industrial applications, proudly serving the Moncton, Riverview, Dieppe, Shediac, Bouctouche, Memramcook, Hillsborough, Salisbury, Sackville, Cap Pele, Dorchester, Richibucto and Riverside Albert area. We would love for you to visit our showroom at 118 Albert St.. There, our team can give you personalized advice in purchasing a garage door, an installation that meets the highest industry standards, and unequalled after-sales service thanks to our maintenance and repair program.  

Our full range of products also includes electric garage door openers as well as many other accessories to go with your garage door. Think of us when it comes to buying, installing or repairing any type of garage door.

Our showroom is located at 118 Albert St. suite B in Moncton and is open Monday to Friday 8 AM to 5 PM, Thursday we close at 8 PM (summer hours). 

I invite you to come and visit us, and on behalf of our entire team, I thank you for considering our company. 

Mike Mann
President
Maritime Garage Doors
